{"tid":690084,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"〖天龍八部〗逆命天龍X無盡天龍 開服一週年合區","createTime":"2018-06-04T14:37:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-26T12:55:14.000Z","uid":122217,"like":28,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"d8ca3263f201cd20d0b44f4198e4fad4b0d61e45","tid":690084,"uid":122217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T14:37:08.000Z","msg":"又係我呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以上決定籌備了一段時間<br />\n合服目的主要為了盡量將香港玩家的人流集中 避免出現死城的情況大大減少玩家的遊玩性<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">合服後儲值回點將會分開處理<br />\n假設玩家在兩服曾經儲點 點數將會在新版累積及疊加</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">新版伺服器特色:<br />\n<br />\n帳號139滿等 送VIP2<br />\n<br />\n新手裝內置4石<br />\n<br />\n所有道具均可刷 頂石7石<br />\n<br />\n每月合服紀念抽獎:<br />\n逢3號開始報名 10號抽獎<br />\n人數達一定數量活動才會進行<br />\n<br />\n抽獎玩法:<br />\n會先從已報名角色名單抽出3名玩家 再由幸運輪抽出贈送之道具/元寶<br />\n<br />\n伺服器亦會定期舉辦節日活動 抽獎 贈送元寶不等<br />\n<br />\n同時舉辦閒常互動活動 例如擊殺特定BOSS獲取道具</span><br />\n<br />\n完整客戶端<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://tl3.xyz/download.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftl3.xyz%2Fdownload.php&d=Gwc0yh0AxeX0MQ0u4gr1AQhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=6e8898ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">tl3.xyz/download.php</a><br />\n<br />\n登陸器補丁包<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://tl3.xyz/download_update.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftl3.xyz%2Fdownload_update.php&d=Gwc0yh0AxeX0MQ0u4gr1AQhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=a3514c39\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://tl3.xyz/download_update.php</a><br />\n<br />\n聯絡方法 (Telegram 和 Discord共通橋樑) :<br />\n<br />\nTG谷: <a href=\"https://t.me/wjtlbbgp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fwjtlbbgp&d=Gwc0yh0AxeX0MQ0u4gr1AQhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=33fb84aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/wjtlbbgp</a> (GM: Silent, Cc)<br />\n<br />\nTG Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/wjtlbb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fwjtlbb&d=Gwc0yh0AxeX0MQ0u4gr1AQhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=ffbb645b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/wjtlbb</a><br />\n<br />\nDiscord: <a href=\"https://discord.gg/Y9hXy4D\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdiscord.gg%2FY9hXy4D&d=Gwc0yh0AxeX0MQ0u4gr1AQhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=5a79db3a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://discord.gg/Y9hXy4D</a> (GM: Lolipop)<br />\n<br />\n基本介紹<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">上線30級, 經驗50倍，心法全119 \n同步官服最新時裝  璃景幻羽  最新坐騎璃翼  bb蛋蛋雞，招財錦狐等等 \n重要的事情說三遍 同步所有官服最新時裝坐騎bb  幻世武器等等\n吃上雙倍經驗，古墓-地宮4-五方境，升級速度極快。\n每晚開啟寶藏洞活動-與五方境活動可使大家獲得大量元寶道具\n獨創子女功能，新進階動作，秘籍等等\n\n（本服所以材料都可在所有場景刷到只要你有時間散人也能變身高富帥）\n本服獨創100級手工套裝，精通屬性可通過90套裝進行轉移\n洛陽開放太古神器打造npc坐標（230.111），vip6級玩家可直接到錢莊進行兌換\n每個太古神器開放10個附體轉換 添加其他私服所沒有的幻蝶 幻羽 霸魂（天山神器帶有）附體\n並添加絢麗稱號兌換洛陽（274,110），vip可直接到錢莊兌換\n\n本服杜絕一切不公平行為,努力做到不給比例。\n不拉團隊,努力營造一個綠色且公平的天龍私服。 </code></pre><br />\n<br />\n詳細介紹/設定: <a href=\"http://tl3.xyz/v1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftl3.xyz%2Fv1%2F&d=Gwc0yh0AxeX0MQ0u4gr1AQhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=c8681157\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://tl3.xyz/v1/</a><br />\n<br />\n有咩意見即管發表<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d0bead0f75b9315cfb56bf7f48c88a3b51b835a","tid":690084,"uid":166374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T05:11:03.000Z","msg":"樓主又係我啦 想問下個登陸器點解係copy完啲嘢過去之後會無咗個launch.exe既"},{"pid":"6ab75241124d10dfa4b6b1d719bb2137ab03e338","tid":690084,"uid":122217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d0bead0f75b9315cfb56bf7f48c88a3b51b835a","tid":690084,"uid":166374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T05:11:03.000Z","msg":"樓主又係我啦 想問下個登陸器點解係copy完啲嘢過去之後會無咗個launch.exe既"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T05:54:07.000Z","msg":"完整客戶端可以直接下載開黎玩<img sr